dubbeyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) walax, dubbe la dhicid oo ku garaacid. Birtu dubbaynta way ku faaxdaa.
dubbeysan: (tilmaame) dubbe lala dhacay oo la tumay.
dubbeysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dubbe lala dhacay ahaan.
dubbeysni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dubbe lala dhacay ahaan.
dubbo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) nooc xawaashka ka mid ah oo sida xabxabka u baxda midheheeduna xabxaka iyo uubada le'ekaado oo inta la qashiro soos laga dhigo ama lagu daro. Anoo aale gooray soo cunay bay; ka dig dheh! dubbadiina ii taal. Dh: aaraadubbe.
dubbur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) neefqabataw lala xuurtoobo. Dh: afto, dubburyo.
dubburyo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) afto nakhaska la soo saari kari waayo. Dh: xuurtood.
dubburyoo: (fal) xuurtoo oo nakhasku ha kugu dhego. Dh: hiinraag, xuurtoo.
dubburyood: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) neefqabataw nakhaska la soo bixin kari waayo. Muquurtu waxay keeni kartaa dubburyood. Dh: neefqabatow.
dubdhac: -a: (magac, lab, keli) marka noole ama shay dubka sare ka baxo. Dh: diirdhac.
dubdhacsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) isbeddel ku yimaadda maqaarka noolaha oo uu diirku ka baxo. Dh: diirdhacsi.
dubid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dab dushii wax ku solid.
dubis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dab dushii wax ku solis. Dubistaa ka xumaatay hilibka ee ku celiya.
dublad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dun noocyo kala duwan leh oo faanuusyada iyo maashooyada gaaska lagu shubo laguna shito oo kolka dab la qabadsiiyo iftiinta. Dh: dubaalad, dibaarad.
dubnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax la dubay oo dab lagu bisleeyey ahaan. Xasiidda dubnaan iyo karsanaanba waa lagu cunaa.
dubnad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciyaar sida turubka fadhiga loogu ciyaaro oo lagu ciyaaro 28 wasladood oo yaryar oo lambarro leh. Dh: dumnad.
dubnax: -a: (magac, lab, keli) naxariis qaraabannimo ama beni'aadannimo. Dh: naxariis.
dubo: (fal) xasiid, hilib ama wax kale, dhamac dul saar oo adoon biyo iyo weel midna isticmaalin toos dhamacda ugu bislayso.
dubri: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qofka ay habaryartaa dhasho. Dh: habrawadaag, ilmadubri.
dubuq: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) si ismoogaan ah biyo ugu dhacid. Dubuq buu yidhi ilmihii berkeddii biyaha ahayd. Dh: dalaq, dhubuq
dubur: (tilmaame) hadba meesha aad joogto halka ugu danbaysa.
dubuur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qof aan weji furneyn oo cabuus ah.
Ducaale: magac loo baxsho will duco ku dhashay ama loo arko in uu yahay qof duco qaba oo barakaysan.
ducaqabe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof wanaagsan, naxariis badan oo bulshadu ka raalli noqotay. Dh: khayrqabe, baarri. Li: habaarqabe.
ducayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) Eebbe baryid iyo wax waydiisigiisa.
ducaysan: (tilmaame) qof loo duceeyey oo doobir qaba.
ducayso: (fal) Ilaahay weydiiso wax fiican. Ducayso dadkana saamax. Dh: Allabari.
ducee: (fal) Eebbe bari; Rabbi tuug. Li: habaar.
duceeye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof dadka alle u barya.
duceyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) Ilaahay baryid oo duco sacabbada u taagid. Dh: ducayn.
duceysad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) duco samaysasho. Dh: ducaysad; ducaysasho.
duceysan: (tilmaame) mid duco qaba oo khayrfalaw ah. Li: habaaran.
duceysi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) Ilaahay baryid oo wax wanaagsan weydiisa.
duceysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid duco iyo khayrqaba ahaan. Dh: ducaysnaan. Li: habaarnaan.
duceysni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid duco iyo khayrqaba ahaan.
duceyso: (fal) Ilaahay wanaag bari xumana ka magan gal. Allaa deeq hayee duceyso.
ducfi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) tamartdarrada iyo itaalxumida qofka ku dhacda jidha ahaan.
duco: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ereyada san ee Ilaahay lagu baryo sharkana lagaga magangalo. Duco waalid ma baaqato. Dh: Allaabari, Alla-tuug. Li: habaar, inkaar.
Duco: magac loo baxsho gabadh edeb badan ama hooyadeed dhali jirin oo kolkii loo duceeyay dhashay.
dud: (fal) cadho kaga tag ciddii aad danwadaagta ahaydeen; cadho kaga tag lammaanahaad u dhaxday. Dh: umal.
dud: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) biyo yar oo weel biyood salkiisa ku jira. Dh: duuddo.
Duda: magac ama naanays loo baxsho gabadh dhalatay hooyadeed oo dudmo ku maqan ama dabeecad xun iyo cadho lagu arkay.
duddeyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka aqal Soomaali loo samaynayo fadhiisin gudaha ah. Aqalku dudeyn wanaagsan u samee. Dh: dahayn.
duddo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel dhan walba laga xego oo badhtan ah. Nin la doonayaa duddo kuma jiro.
duddoyaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) alaabta muhiimka ah ee raarta aqalka la dhigo. Li: dibadyaal.
duddumaggale: -ha: (magac, dhedig, keli) naasley dabagaallaha la bah ah oo ka roon, kooxkooxna u socota inteeda badan. Dh: dundumagale, kadabjiir.
duddumo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kuus ciid ah oo siyaabo kala duwan u samaysan oo aboorku dhiso. Dh: dundumo.
duddumodibir: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) duddumada aboorka dibirka ku nooli sameeyo oo duldulleelo badan dusha ku leh. Dh: dundumodibir.
Duddun: magac loo baxsho wiil ku garab dhashay duddun. Waxa kale ee loo baxshaa wiil dhashay isaga oo buurri darteed dundumo la moodo.
duddun: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciid uu aboorku qandhuuftiisa ku qooyo oo inta uu dhoobo ka dhigo, dhis weyn ka sameeyo. Duddun dheeraataaba way dumi. Dh: dundumo, dudumo.
dudduub: (fal) wax fidsan isku celceli oo dhawr jeer isku laallaab. Dh: duuduub, laalaab.
dudduub: (tilmaame) war iyo wax la mid ah, guud ahaan.
dudduub -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax fidsanaa, laallaabistiisa.
dudduubasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax fidsanaa, dhawr jeer laallaabasho.
dudduubid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) isku laalaabid ama wax kale ku moqollofid. Hadiyaddu dudduubidda ayay ku qurxoon tahay. Dh: duuduubid.
Dude: magac ama naanays loo baxsho wiil dhashay hooyadii oo dudmo ku maqan ama dabeecad xun iyo cadho lagu arkay.
dude: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ninka marka uu cadhoodo ba ka taga reerkiisa. Dude maantana ma maqanyahey.
dudi: (fal) ka xanaaqsii oo inuu cadho ku socdo sabab u ahaw. Dh: dudsii.
dudid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ka tegidda halkaad degganayd adiga oo cadho qaba. Dudidda badani reerkaagay dumisaa. Dh: ulmid.
dudin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid ka xanaaqsiin oo inuu cadho ku socdo sabab u noqosho.
dudmo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) socod cadho lagu tago oo inta wixii cadhada keenay la xallinayo la soo noqon waayo. Dudmo ayay dumaashiday ku magan tahay.
dudsanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid dudmo ku maqan ahaan.
dudsani: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid dudmo ku maqan ahaan.
dudsasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) eryesho reerka la caymadsado.
dudubi: (fal) si degdeg ah wax ucun. Dudubi qadada ragbaa ku sugayee.
dudubin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka cunto si dhakhso ah loo cunayo ama hadal la daldalayo. Cuntadu dudubinta kuma fiicna ee miyir u cun Dh: dedejin.
duf: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) maydhaxda kabadda laga sameeyo ee la budliyey ee aan la soohine filiqsan oo gas badan leh. Laba minjood oo dufah baan maleegay saaka oo qudha.
duf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) xanuun dadka seedaha cagta kaga dhaca oo daalka badani sababo. Duf baa i dilay duugmo ku filanna ma helin.
duf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) bulka shaashka ah ee kebeddu dhanka dambe ku leedahay. Kebedda dufkiibaa ka dhammaaday.
duf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhogorta adhiga ee cufan gaar ahaan ta uu iska gooyo xiilliga uu dhogorgoosanayo. Dufka ka jar laxda.
duf-ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) alaab raagtay oo calal noqotay. Wixii duf ah ee gaboobay naga daadiya.
duf -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) xumaan dhibaato laga Allabaryo. Duf iyo wax daran Alloo naga hay. Dh: balaayo.
dufan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wixii dux leh ama oon xoolaad. Dh: subag.
dufanayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dufan marin ama ku idaamid. Jimcabarkhadluhu waa maalinta dufanaynta geesaha lo'da.
dufanee: (fal) cunto yaabis ah subag ku dar; wax basaasay subag mari. Dh: subagee.
dufanle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof had iyo jeer jidhkiisu iyo hugiisu subkan yahay.
dufantirasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dufan iska tirid oo iska masaxid.
dufantiryo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dufan ama cunto kooban oo yar. Dh: dhaarshil. dufay: (tilmaame) madhay oo hiigmay.
dufayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dullayn oo wax horay u fiicnaa xumayn.
dufaysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid dulli iyo basaas qaba ahaan. Dufaysnaan badan baa dushiisa ka muuqatay markaan bariidiyey shalay.
dufaysnaan -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax la dufeeyey oo bul loo yeelay ahaan. Maydhaxda kebedda laga sameeyo dufaysnaanta waa loogu talagalay.
dufe: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) dhogorta idaha ama bulka maydhaxda.
dufee: (fal) duf ka dhig. Maydhaxda aad kebedda ku samaynayso dugfee.
dufee: (fal) xumee oo sidii hore si ka sii liidata ka dhig.
duf'idaad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhogorta idaha. Funaanadaha duf'idaadda idahaa laga sameeyaa. Dh: dhogor'idaad.
duflaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qofka dadka isagoo aan u kala aabbayeelin af iyo addinba ku xumeeya. Dh: nacas, doqon, caran, dabbaal, coon, caqligaab.
duflaxood: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) waqtiga sumalka lagu daro idiha.
dufmin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) duf u yeelid; dunta oo inta shaal loo yeelo cidhifka go'yaasha laga lulo. Dunta guudka iyo shaalka waa loo dufminayaaye. Dh: fadhqin, dufayn.
dufni: (fal) wax la dufeeyey oo bul duf leh laga dhigay ahaan.
dufoobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulloobid oo sidii hore ka sii liidasho. Dh: humoobid, calaloobid.
dufow: (fal) dullow oo sidii hore si ka sii liidata ahaw.
dug: (ereycodeed) dibida loo adeegsado oo ah in yar hore u soco.
dugaag: -ga: (magacwadareed) magaca guud ee xayawaanka duurjoogta ah ee hilibkunoosha loo yaqaan. Dh: duurjoog. wuxuush. Li: dabjoog.
dugaagad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) garaarro ama walax wareegsan oo dahab, qalin ama wax kale ka samaysan oo dumarku gamcaha gashadaan oo isku qurxiyaan. Dh: jijin, shuuli.
dugaagnimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dugaag wax cuna ahaan.
dugaagoobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dugaag noqosho; sida dugaagga u dhaqmid.
dugaagow: (fal) dugaag noqo ama sida dugaagga u dhaqan.
dugaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gabbaad dhaxanta ama cadceedda laga galo. Dh: dugsi. Li: daleed.
dugaalso: (fal) wax aad dhibaato ka gabbaadsato ka dhigo.
dugaanti: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) godka 27aad ee godadka dayaxu fadhiisto.
dugayo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhibaato muuqata oo baahi keentay.
dugdug: dugdug -ga: (magac, lab, keli) socodka qof gaboobay oo horey loo sii dhacdhaco. Dh: luud.
dugduglayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka qof u socdo si tamaryari ah oo uu hore u sii dhacdhaco. Dugduglayn buu halkan ku soo gaadhay.
dugey: erey uu ku calaacalo ama uu ku ooyo qof ay dhib weyni ku dhacday. Dh: jagay! hoogay! ba'ay! ba'ayaalay!
dugid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ba' iyo ba'ayaale la kulmid. Dh: hoogid.
dugsad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhaxan kaga gabbasho oo dugsi ka dhigasho. Dh: dugaalsad, dugsash.
dugsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) meel aan dhaxan, dabayl iyo qorrax toona lahayn. Dugsi ma leh gabyaaladi, waxay dumiso mooyaane. Dh: hoy, baro, bayd, aqal, guri.
dugsi-ga: (magac, lab, keli) meel wax lagu barto, barayaal iyo arday timaaddo oo wax la isku baro oo maammul leh; goob waxbarasho.
dugsii: (fal) dhaxant, dabaysha, roobka iyo cadawga ka jir ama ka ilaali.
dugsiin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhaxanta, roobka, dabaysha, roobka iyo cadawga ka jirid ama ka ilaalin.
Dugsiiya: magac loo baxsho gabadh hooyadeed rajaynayso in ay ku nasato.
Dugsiiye: magac loo baxsho wiil dhashay hooyadii oo aan dhalin ama gabdho uun lahayd.
dugso: (fal) meel ka gal dhaxanta iyo dabaylaha; cid kale wehesho oo cadawga ka taageerso.
dugsoon: (tilmaame) meel aanay dhaxan iyo dabayl midna jirin oo roobka iyo qorraxdaba celisa. Dh: diirran. Li: qabow.
dugsoonaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) diirranaan oo dugsi dhaxanta celiya ahaan.
dugukuur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) socod meel aan kala fogayn loo kala socdo.
dugul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) midab aad u madow.
Dugul: magac loo baxsho wiil madaw u dhashay.
Dugulo: magac loo baxsho gabadh madow u dhalatay.
dugyar: (ereydhawaaq) loo adeegsado kolka laba dibi beer lagu qodayo inay hal tallaabo xagga hore u qaadan. Dugyar dheh dibida oo faagga gaadhsii halkiisii.
Duhur: magac loo baxsho wiilka dhasha xilli dharaar ah oo salaad duhur ah.
duhur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) maalinta badhtameheeda; xilliga salaadda duhur la tukado ilaa inta casar laga gaadhayo.
duhuri: (fal) horey ha u kallihin. Duhuri xoolaha dharabku haka kacee. Dh: bariisii. Li: jarmaadi.
duhursasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dib u dhicid illaa ay cadceeddu kululaanayso ama duhur noqonayso. Dh: dharaarsasho.
duhurso: (fal) dib u dhac oo ha bixin illaa ay cadceeddu kululaanayso ama duhur noqonayso Dh: dharaarso.
duji: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) doorada dhedig. Dh: digaagad.
dujin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) baabi'in oo cidhib jarid.
dujin-ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhammaystirid o wax soo afjarmay ka dhigid. Bil baa ka hadhay dujinta mashruuca. Dh: ebyid, dhammaystirid.
dukaafad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qashinka la tuuro iyo halka lagu daadiyoba. Dh: guddaafad, kuddaafad, qashin.
dukaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) meherad wax lagu iibiyo oo si joogta ah looga shaqeeyo. Dukaanka kabriid iiga soo iibi. Dh: tukaan.
dukaanle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof tukaan wax lagu iibiyo leh ama ka shaqeeya, Dh: tukaanle.
dukaansaar: (fal) dukaan ku dar dukaan kale oo meesha sii ahaa.
dukaansaarid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka dukaan hore mid kale lagu daro kaas oo aanay isku wax iibinaynin laakiin wada socon karaan oo wada iibsamayaan.
dukaanso: (fal) suuqa alaabo kala duwan ka soo iibso. Dh: adeego.
dukad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) salaad Ilaahay la imasho oo cibaado ahaan u oogid. Dh: dukasho.
dukasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) salaad Ilaahay la imasho oo cibaado ahaan u oogid. Dh: tukasho.
dukhsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cayayaan duula oo lix lugood leh oo ku tarma meelaha qudhunka iyo guddaafaddaha.
dukhun: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) jaad sarciga la quuto ka mid ah oo firi yaryar leh oo agagaarka. Dh: tukhun.
dukhuun: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dad ama xoolo aad u gaboobay oo tabar dhigay. Dh: sirqo.
duko: (fal) salaad la imo oo hor Ilaahay is taag. Kol haddaad gaan gaadhay duko. Dh: tuko.
dul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) labada dalool ee sanka midkood. Dul baa i xidhan caawa oo duray baa i haya.
dul-sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) oogada sare; xagga sare ee korka ah. Dh: kor. Li: hoos.
dul: (tilmaame) guud ahaan; si guud. Dul ahaan dhulku waa nabad.
dul-sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulqaad, adakaysi iyo xilkasnimo uu Ilaahay qof siiyo. Maxamed waa nin dul badan. Dh: dulqaad.
dul -sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) halka dumarku fooddada ku xidhaan ee dhexda ah, halkaas oo ay qadhaabka iyo maydhaxda ku ritaan. Dh: faraq, nabas.
dulaami: (fal) dhinac u rid. Dh: ciirsii, dullaami, dilaami.
dulaamin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax taagan, dhinac u ridid.
dulaandul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) labada cad ee duudka ka raaca adhaxda hareeraheeda. dulaaqan: (tilmaame) mid afka ilkihii ka daateen ama ka dhammaadeen.
dulalaati: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cabsi aan wax la arkayo laga baqayn. Dulalaati geeluba mar buu digigixoodaaye. Dh: cabsi.
dulayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dul sarraysa u yeelid.
dulayn -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulli iyo xaqiraad badid oo u sabibi.
dulaysani: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid dulli qaba ahaan.
dulaysnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) xaqiraad iyo dulli qabitaan.
dulbaa'i: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) jiho fog oo meel dheer ka muuqata. Dh: xag, dhan, dhinac, jiho.
dulbaax: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hilibka dhabarka ku yaalla ama awlallada ka sarreeya.
dulbadi: (fal) dulqaado oo qaladdo ama dhibaatooyin u dhabar'adayg. Dh: adkayso.
dulbadi-da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulqaad iyo adkaysi yeelasho. Dh: adkaysasho.
dulbadni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulqaad badnaan. Dh: dulqaad.
dulbax: (fal) fuul faras ama geed iyo wixii la mid ah. Ha dulbixin intaan heemin hanta caanahae.
dulbeel: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) adkaysi la'aan iyo dulqaad waayid.
dulbeel -ka: (magac, lab, keli) xamilgab muurka ku dhaca kolka uu nabar dhabarka ama garbaha ka soo baxo, rar si xun loo raray darteed. Dh: dhabarbeel, garbabeel.
dulbeelid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) muur la rarto, garbabeelid; xamilgabid oo dusha nadar ku yeelasho. Dh: garbabeelid.
dulcade: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) gorgorweyn oo dusha diilin cad ku leh. Dh: gorgor.
dulcade -ha: (magac, lab, keli) duq weyn oo guradu caddaatay. Dulcadde waa laga dambeeyaa.
dulcayaarid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) «ku cid kale dusheeda ku ciyaarid. Dh: dulciyaarid.
dulci: (fal) xadhig dulac ah geli. Intay googgaradda dulcinaysay buu dherigii ka gubtay.
dulciir: (fal) si awood la'aan ah shay korkiisa ugu dhac.
dulcin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka googgarad ama daah loo samaynayo xadhig dhexda ka gala oo lagu xidho oo xajiya.
duldhig: (fal) shey, wax kale korkiisa dhig. Buugga miiska duldhig.
duldhig: (fal) deyn lagaa qaatay macaash dheeri ah saaro.
duldhig-ga: (magac, lab, keli) macaash dheeri ah oo deymaha la saaro. Shareecadda Islaamku duldhigga baananka ribo ayay ku tirisaa. Dh: dulsaar.
duldhigid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax kor saarid oo dushiisa dhigid.
duleed: duleed -ka: (magac, lab, keli) reerka agagaarkiisa, meel aan aqallada ka durugsanayn. Dh: kambal.
duleedi: duleedi: (fal) labo qof oo is dilaya mid garabsii oo u duleedi ka kale.
duleedin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhabarjebin samayn oo ciidan sii jeeda dagaal xagga dambe kaga keenid.
duleel: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) meel hoos u qodan ama daloosha. Soomaalaay dareenlay, boholaha duleeliyo, deylaanta loo qoday, dusha maro ka saaraay. Dh: dalool.
duleel -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax isku sigib tiran meel yar oo furan oo ka bannaan. Duleelka dhegta waxa la geliyaa hilqad. Dh: dalool.
duleeli: (fal) duleel u samee; meel xidhan in yar ka bannee oo fur. Gabadha yar dhegta u duleeli. Dh: dalooli.
duleelid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel in yar ka furantahay ahaan. Dh: daloolid.
duleelin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel, in yar oo dalool ah ka furid. Dh: duleelin.
duleeliye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) wax, wax lagu duleeliyo oo meel xidhan lagu banneeyo. Kabatoluhu waa duleeliye.
duleeshan: (tilmaame) meel, in yar oo ka bannaan ama furan leh. Weel duleeshan biyo ma celiyo. Dh: dalooshan.
duleeshanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel ama weel, in yar oo ka bannaan ama furan ahaan. Dh: dalooshanaan.
dulfadhi: (fal) qof nafka'eeg ah ama wax inuu daranyoobaa halis ay tahay ilaali oo la joog.
dulfadhi -ga: (magac, lan, keli) qof sankaraad ah la joogid oo xaalkiisa ka warhayn.
dulfadhi -ga: (magac, lan, keli) ciidan ciidan kale uu dhawaan ku duuli lahaa soo duldega oo meel gaaban u barya.
dulfadhiyid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid bugta la joogid.
dulfadhiyid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel la weerarayo agbaryid.
dulgee: (fal) cid meel ka kaxee oo cid meel kale joogta dul jooji.
dulin: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) shilinta ku dhalata xoolaha ee ku nool dhiigooda iyo dheecaankooda. Dh: qaniin, dulan.
duljoogid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) jid liidata oo bukaan ah, dulfadhiyid.
dulkadhaw: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dusha ka garaacid. Dh: korkadhaw. Li: hooskadhaw.
dulkasocoto: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dad safar ah oo ku soo beegmay reerka xilli cunto aanay jirin. Dulkasocotada dheri cusub u dhadhaara.
dulkaxaabin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax buuxa oo dusha sare laga xaadiyo. Dh: korkaxaadin.
dulkaxaabis: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dulka xaabin. Dulkaxaabis mooyee arrin kale ma hayside iga tag.
dulkaxaadi: (fal) wax si fudud uga kor qaad wax kale oo uu dusha ka saaran yahay adigoon ka hoose taaban.
dulkaxaadin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) si khafiif ah uga qaadid. Dh: dulkaxaadis.
dulkaxaadis: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) inta sare aayar uga qaadid. Kolka la goolabo hadhuudhka ayay dulkaxaadistu dhib yar tahay.
dulkaxaadis -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadal dul marid oo xaqiiqada dhabta ah guudka ka marmarid. Dh: dulkaxaadin.
dulkuneefle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) noole kaste oo hawada ka qaata sanka. Dh: sankuneefle.
dullaal: (fal) dad wax la kala iibsanaya u dhexee labada dhinac. Dh: dillaal.
dullaalid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolo labo dhinac kala iibsanayaan, u dhaxayn oo dillaalid.
dullaalnimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dillaal shaqo ka dhigasho.
dullaamid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhan u ciirid oo u wiliilsamid. Dh: ciirid.
dullaamo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciiridda uu shay dhan u ciiro.
dullaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax culus oo taagan, dhan u ciiris oo dhicid. Haddaad maanta dullaanto oo uu daayeerkaasi ku laayo, anna saw dumi maayo.
dullaandul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) labada cad ee dhabarka hareeraha ka raaca. Dullaandulkaa xidid.
dullalaati: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) dalool yar oo ka bannaan wax is haysta ama jiq oo cirku muuqdo iga hayaa. Dh: dululaati.
dulinduleed: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) noole dulin ah oo soorihiisa dusha kaga nool.
dulingudeed: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) noole dulin ah oo soorihiisa ku dhex nool.
dullay: (fal) ka dhig wax aan nadiif ahayn oo xaqiran.
dullayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof sharafta ka dhigid oo qayrkii ka reebid.
dullayn -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dibi iyo wixii la mid ah, dulle la dhicid.
dullaysani: -da: (mafac, dhedig, keli) wax la xaqiray oo dulleeyey ahaan. Dh: dullaysanaan.
dulle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) ul dheer oo suun amaba xadhig ku xidhan yahay oo lagu kaxeeyo dibida marka beerta lagu qodayo. Dh: shaabuug.
dullee: (fal) dibi iyo wixii la mid ah, dulle la dhac.
dullee: (fal) qof sharaftiisa dil, xaqir oo wax bahdilan oo dulli ah ka dhig.
dulleysasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, sida addoonnada ugu adeegsasho oo xaqdarro ugu amarkutaaglayn.
dulleyso: (fal) sida addoonnada ula dhaqan o0 xaqdarro ugu amarkutaaglee.
dulli: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) bahdilnaan iyo dacdatarro cid ka muuqata. Dulli lama hillaabtee; aaway hanaddadaadii.
dulli -ga: (magac, lab, keli) qof dullinimo aqbala.
dulloobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) daranyo iyo dacdarro la ba'yaalid; dulli noqosho.
dullow: (fal) sharaftaadu ha dhimato; xushamaddaadu ha guurto. Dh: daranyow.
dulmadow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) jaad dacawada ka mid ah oo diilinta sare madaw. Dh: deyo.
dulmanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) mid la dulmay oo caddaaladxumo lagu sameeyey ahaan.
dulmane: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof xaquu lahaa la duudsiyey.
dulmar: (fal) dusha sare u dhaaf, ku dul soco.
dulmar: (fal) isha mari oo akhris degdeg ah ku samee. Qoraalkan ii dulmar inta aana gudbinin.
dulmar: (fal) weel geed laga qorayo is khafiif ah qoraal ku ekee. Gaawaha waa la dulmaray oo qoraal danbe uma laabna ee aabeeya.
dulmar -ka: (magac, lab, keli) gudinquraar si khaafiif ah u marin weel la qorayo. Dulmar bay u baahantahay dhiishu si ay quruxdeedu u soo baxdo. Dh: kormar.
Dulmar: magac loo baxsho gabadh laga filayo inay qurux iyo habdhaqan ba dumarka dhaafto.
dulmari: (fal) shey kor mari wax kale. Xadhigga kooraanka dulmari guriga. Dh: kormari. Li: hoosmari.
dulmarid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dushiisa marid oo ka sarrayn. Dulmaridda xadhkaha korantadu waa halis.
dulmarid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadal aan toos ahayn oo sarbeeb ah odhasho; hadal guudmar ah dhihid. Dadka waaweyni dulmaridda ayay wax ku fahmaan.
dulmarin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) xagga sare ka marin, korka ka marin.
dulmi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax aan jid ahayn, aan cidina raalli ka ahayn in nafteeda loo gaysto. Dh: xaqdaro, gardarro. Li: xaq, gar, caddaalad.
dulmid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulan iyo gardarro kula dhaqmid dadka kale.
dulmin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid ku gefid oo caddaaladdarro kula dhaqmid.
dulmiyid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, si xaqdarro ah ugu xadgudbid. Dh: dulmin.
dulnool: (tilmaame) cid kale, dulsaar ku ahaan oo ku dul noolaansho. Dh: dulsaar.
dulnoolaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel dusheeda ku noolaan.
dulnoolaan -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, la galid oo dulsaar ku ahaan.
dul'ordid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax, dushiisa ku ordid. Dh: dulcaymadid.
dulqaad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) awoodda degganaashaha kolka dhibi timaad iyo samirka. dulqaadad -ka: (magac, lab, keli) akaysad oo dhib ama xadgudub iska saamixid. Dh: dhabar'adaygid.
dulqaadasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kolka qofku ximmilaad muujiyo oo dhibaatooyinka u adkaysto.
dulqaadbadni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) adkaysi badnaan oo dulmi ama xadgudub kale iska saamixid.
dulqaado: (fal) marka lagu xumeeyo ama lagugu gefo is xakamee oo naftaada.
dulsaar: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) lacagta dulsocodka ah ee bangiyada qaarkood dul dhigtaan ciddii lacag ka amaahata ama lacagtaad dhigatay lacag ay ku sii dhashay jid aan sharciga islaamka waafaqsanayn. Dh: ribo.
dulsaaran: (tilmaame) dushiisa saaran oo koryaal. Dh: dulyaal.
dulsaarasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) duldhigashada aad wax duldhigato meel.
dulsaarid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dushiisa saarid oo ka korraysiin. Dh: duldhigid.
dulsaarid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) macaash la isla og yahay deyn qof kaa qaaday ku kordhin. Dh: duldhigid.
dulsaarnaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) shey wax kale dulsaaran ahaan. Miiska dulsaarnaanta ka fudaydi.
dulsabbayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax fudud, biyo korkooda socosho. Nin aan dabbaal aqoon dulsabaynta kari maayo.
dulsabbee: (fal) biyo dushooda saarnaw oo dhaqdhaqaaq la'aan dul ool.
dulsoco: (fal) wax korkiisa ku taltallaabso. Kaabadda miyir u dulsoco oo ha ka dhicin. Dh: dulmar.
dulsocod: dulsocod -ka: (magac, lab, keli) waxa lagu kordhiyo deyn la kala amaahdo ee duldhigga ah.
duluc: -a: (magac, lab, keli) daliig maro ah oo dhexda laga soo geliyo googgaradda dumarka ama daahyada oo lagu xidho ama xajisa. Dulucu hadduu go' googgaradduna way kaa dhici doontaa.
duluc-da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ujeeddo ama nuxur uu hadal leeyahay.
dulucsan: (tilmaame) daah ama googgarad, duluc 10 bibno u leh.
dulugle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) caydhoobid cayn xoolaad la waayo iyo maal ka hoogid. Dh: boglaawe.
dululaati: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) meel banaan oo labadhexaad ah; meel hud ama labo geed isugu yimaaddaan.
dululici: (fal) walax wareegsan meel kala dheer ku riix. Si taxadar leh u dululici foostada. Dh: dilindillee.
dululicin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) walax wareegi karta aayar ku socodsiin meel hoos u foorarta.
dululub: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dareere meel ku gembin.
dululubo: (tilmaame) wax dhuuban oo dheer. Dh: dhululubo.
dululuc: -a: (magac, lab, keli) dhul sii kala hooseeya. Dululuca mari foostada giraamaha leh oo wilaanwili.
duluf: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) derin, jawaan, raar, iyo wixii la mid ah oo duugoobay. Dh: duruf.
dulufaaq: -a: (magac, lab, keli) si dan la'aan ah hore iyo gadaal ugu socosho.
dulun: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) xadgudub iyo caddaalad la'aan. Dh: dulmi, dulan.
dulundulcee: (fal) sida daadka u soco. Dixda daadkiibaa dulundulcaynaaya caawa baabuurrana ma mari karaan.
dulundulceyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) sida biyaha u socosho.
dulundulceysii: (fal) suluulixi oo sida biyaha u dhaqaaji.
dulundulceysiin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) suluuluxin oo sida biyaha u dhaqaaqsiin.
dulundulco: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhaqdhaqaaqa ay biyaha ama masasku sameeyaan.
duluqbay: (tilmaame) qof wax aan khusayn iyo meel walba ku dhaca oo aan xishoon.
duluqlayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) socod uu qof kolba meel aan laga rabin galgalo.
duluqle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka meel walba oo aan loo oggolayn ama raalli looga ahayn gala.
dulwadh: (fal) shey ku dul kala baxi meel ama wax kale kale. Go'a ku dulwadh xadhiga.
dulxaadi: (fal) wax meel yaal ama weel ku jira. dusha sare ka yara qaadid.
dulxaadi: (fal) arrin hoos ha uqu dhaadhicin. Li: doox.
dulxawaaree: ( fal) xoog u dul caymad; aad u dul'orod.
dulxawaareyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) aad u dul'ordid; xoog u dul caymadid.
dulxumo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) foolxumaan ama ilxumaan. Dh: ilxumo.
dulxun: (tilmaame) qaab aan fiicnayn leh. Dh: foolxun.
dulyar: (tilmaame) qof dulqaad yar oo aan gefka qaadan karin. Dh: dulqaadyar.
dulyaraan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulqaad yaraan aan gefka la qaadan karin.
dulyari: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dulqaadyari aan gefka loo dulqaadan.
dulyeelad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dulweynaan dadka gefefkooda loo adkaysto; dulqaad badaan.
dulyeelo: (fal) dulqaado oo gefefka dadka dul iyo nabas u yeelo. Dh: dulqaado.
dumaa: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) caws gugii baxay dayrtuna aanay helin ama dhedo ku dhacday oo madoobaadey.
dumaal: (fal) haweenay walaalkaa ama nin xigaal ah ka dhintay guurso.
dumaal -ka: (magac, lab, keli) haweenay ninkeegii ka geeriyooday oo uu guursaday walaalkii ama nin xigtadiisa ah, wiilka ay dhasho.
dumaal -sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) haweenay ninkeegii ka geeriyooday oo uu guursaday walaalkii ama nin xigtadiisa ah. Dumaal nin ka xishooday kama dhalo, Li: bilcan.
dumaalid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gabadh nimaad xigto tihiin ka dhintay guursashadeeda.
dumaashi: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) haweenayda walaalkaa qabo ama gabadha saygaga la dhalatay.
dumar: -ka: (magacwadareed) dadka inta dhedig. Dumar iyo haween baa nolol lagu hawaystaa.
dumar -ka: (magacwadareed) qayb ka mid ah minanka faalka, waana afar min oo kala ah: Minsubagle, Inkays, Bayaad iyo Uqle.
dumayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dad abaabulid oo soo ururin.
dumbuluq: (ereycodeed) lagu tilmaansado shanqadha wax biyo ku dhax dhacay sida dhagax oo kale.
dumbuluq -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhul kala sarsarreeya oo socodka ku adag.
dumbuq: -a: (magac, lab, keli) qori fudud oo hubka lagu dagaallamo ka mid ah. Dh: bunduq.
dumburyo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cagta oo xoog wax loogu dhufto. Dumburyada qarsoon iyo docdocaynta kala hadha, ka danbaxana kuma talin. Dh: harraati, laad, leed.
dumee: (fal) abaabul oo isku tubbarid, Dh: dun.
dumi: (fal) wax dhisan rid oo dhulka soo dhig. Dh: burburi. Li: dhis.
dumid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) tiro ciidan ah oo meel la isugu keenay. Soo dumidda ciidanka waa inaad horseed adigu ka ahaatid.
dumid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dhisme kala daadin, burburid oo kala daadasho. Dumidda guriga dabayshaa sabab u ahayd.
dumin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, kali) dhisme taagnaa, burburin ama baabi'in. Wax dumin way fudduddahay wax dhisidna way cululstahay. Li: dhisid.
dumis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) burburis ama jajabis dhisme taagnaa.
dummad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) masuuliyad qof dusha ku qaato.
dummad-da: (magac, dhedig, keli) yaanyuur ama bisad.
dummad -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dakhalka doonyaha meesha ugu sarreysa.
dummo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xilqaadasho; wax bixintiisa ama keenistiisa iskorsaarid. Dh: dimmo.
dummudh: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax inta uu aad u gubtay basay ama dubka laga qaaday. Digo roobku qooyoo, dummudh looga guuroo, dulinkii haraaciyey.
dummudh -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax huur dartii la qadhmuunaadey. Hilibku wuu dumudhay.
dumnad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ciyaar ka mid ah ciyaaraha fudud oo labaatan iyo siddeed dhagax oo cadcad oo lambarro leh lagu ciyaaro. Dh: dubnad.
dumudhi: (fal) shey dubka ka qaad. Dumudhi haragga idiin masafta lagu gaaraan ka dhiye.
dumudhin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) harag la qudhminayo oo dhogorta laga saarayo, qudhmin.
dumug: (tilmaame) deegaan dadkii iyo duunyadiiba ka dhamaadeen. Dh: mudug.
dun: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) asal iyo ab, halka ruuxu ka soo jeedo. Waa isku dun oo waa dad walaalo ah. Dh: isir, dunji.
dun-ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) xadhkaha miigmiiqsan ee laga sameeyo dharka. Dadna adaa u qurux badan, dookhna waa ka igu jira, duntuna iigu kaa xiran.
dunayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) dun, meel gelin sida irbad, shawlad ama faynuus.
dunbuq: -a: (magac, lab, keli) nooc qoryaha ka mid ah ciidamadu ku dagaallamaan ee fudfudud. Dh: bunduq, qori.
dundumagale: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) mas halaq ah oo dundumooyinka godad ka samaysta. Dh: duddumaggale.
dundumid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dhisnaa oo taagnaa, burburid oo kolba in ka dumid.
dungo': -a: (magac, lab, keli) wax dunida ka dhammaaday noqo. Dh: sayngo', cayngo', dabargo'.
dungo' -a: (magac, lab, keli) wax dunida ka dhammaaday noqosho. Dungo' buu maroodigii ku noqday dhulka Soomaalida. Dh: sayngo', cayngo'.
dungoo: (fal) shey cidhibtir oo tafiirtir. Dh: sayngoo.
dungul: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) timaha dameeraha iyo gamaanka kale margaagga kaga yaalla.
duni: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) adduunweynaha Ilaahay uumiyaha saaray. Waa duni la kala iibsadoon nala ogaysiine. Dh: adduun. Li: aakhiro.
Duniyo: magac loo baxsho gabadh quruxdii dunida oo dhan lagu metaalay.
dunji: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) halka wax ka soo farcamaan. Dh: asal, isir.
dunle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) marada dunta ka samaysan.
dunmid: -da: (magac; dhedig; keli) abaabulmid oo qof cid wax la wada ahaan. Dh: abaabulmid.
dunnaa: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) caws sannadkii hore ka soo hadhay oo halkii uu ka baxay ku raabuqay.
dunnayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) tantoomid ama feedh la dhicid.
dunnee: (fal) tantoomo la dhac. Dhabarka ka dunnee ha soo jeestee. Dh: tantoon.
dunqaaree: (fal) duunyo aan garaad lahayn ka dhig.
dunqaareyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) duunyo aan garaad lahayn ka dhigid.
dunqaaro: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) abuuraha aan dad ahayn. Dh: duunyo.
dunqar: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qofka ay garashadiisu aad u hooseyso.
dunqulaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) xansaska dabka lagu huriyo. Dunqulaal inoo soo gura aynu dab shidannee.
dunsanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dumay oo isku dhacay ahaan.
dunuuf: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) meesha ay iska galaan gidaarka iyo jiingaddu. Dunuufka adkee yaanay dabayshu jiingadda qaadine.
dunuunuc: -a: (magac, lab, keli) reenka geela kolka isaga oo aan afka kala qaadin uu cod guux ah bixiyo. Dh: nuunaas, guux, gunuunuc, reen.
dunuunucid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hoosta ka guuxid oo sidii ilmo wax diidaya u nuunaasid. Dunuunicidda jooji oo waxaad tabanayso sheego. Dh: gunuunicid.
duq: -a: (magac, lab, keli) noole muddo dheer jirey. Dh: waayeel.
duq -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) ruux dumar ah oo da'weyn ama waayeel ah. Dh: habar. Li: dhoorray.
duqad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gaadhi matoorka waxyeello ka gaadhay ama matoorkiisu dhintay.
duqad-da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hilib lagu ridqay mashiin.
duqadee: (fal) hilib ridiq oo budo ka dhig. Hilibki waa la soo duqadeeyey
duqaw: (fal) duq gaboobay noqo. Dh: duqow, gabaw.
duqee: duqee: (fal) meel ama wax kale, jiidh.
duqeyti: -da: (magacwadareed) dadka da'doodu weyn tahay. Duqeytida ayaa loo tebiyaa wixii go'aan istiraatiiji ah laga qaadanayo. Dh: dugoy.
duqnimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof gaboobay ahaan; da' ahaan.
duqeyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) hub waaweyn bartilmaameed ku garaacid.
duqoobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gabow iyo da weynaan uu nooluhu gaadho. Duqoobid ba ka soo muuqata. Dh: gabow.
duqow: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) gabowga ku yimaadda ruux in badan soo noolaa. Duqowgu dawo ma leh. Dh: gabow.
duqsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cayayaan duula oo meelaha wasakhda aad ugu tarma. Dh: dukhsi.
duqus: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) basbaas ridqan oo midab guguudan leh oo cuntada lagu cuno.
dur: (fal) cid kale, wax caaro fiiqan leh ku mud. Irbadda duumada isku dur oo is dawee. Dh: turuq.
dur -ka: (magac, lab, keli) qoryaha delebka iyo jilfaha tamaanka lagu ciyaaro dhankooda madow ama sare. Durkiyo daabacaba waw dhigaa deleb sidiisiiye. Dh: daabac.
dura: (falkaabe) eray u dhigma beri hore ama waqti hore. Sheekada duxdeedii, carrab dalab li'soo galay, waa xaal ilaa dura, dunidaba ka joogee. Dh: sula.
duraamasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baryo is jilcini ku jirto. Dh: durraansasho.
duraanso: (fal) cid kale hadal u jeedi waano ah ama canaan ah.
duraanso: (fal) cid kale, bari oo tuug.
duray: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) xanuun qufac iyo xummad leh oo inta badan qofka cabbudhiya. Dh: hargab.
durba: (falkaabe) markiiba; isla kolkiiba. Hadalkaan imika lahayn durba idaacaddaa sheegtay.
durbaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) agab ka samaysan xeedho harag afka lagaga tigtigay loona isticmaalo ciyaaraha hiddaha iyo dhaqanka iyo caroosyada. Nin durbaan tumay ilaaq dalbay. Dh: gurbaan, def, narso.
durbaansan: (tilmaame) wax sida durbaanka u samaysan oo wareeg kankoonsan leh. Dh: kankoonsan.
durbaansanaan: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax durbaansan oo sida durbaanka u kankoonsan ahaan.
durdur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) biyo quiqulaya oo si joogto ah u socda. Dixdani waxay leeyahay durdur aan go'in.
durduri: (fal) tirfatirfee oo sida qaalin dheregtey u roor.
durdurid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) dareere, qulqulid oo dhulka dul socosho.
durdurin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) oradka uu sameeyo geelu oo ay dhereg oo farxadi ku jirto, samayn.
durduris: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) orodka geela kolka uu dhergo ee si aan habaysnayn uu cagaha dhulka ula dhaco oo orod iyo boodbood isku daro.
durduro: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) orodka geelu ordo marka uu caleenta iyo barwaaqada ka dhergo. Durduro geel baa ku jaba.
durduur: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) labo goor noqodka biyaha ee xoolaha.
durduurasho: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kolka biyaha xooluhu ka dhergaan ee dib loo marinayo kol labaad. Dh: rakaad, maris. Li: kamiin.
durduuro: (fal) ka dhereg biyo iyo wixii la mid ah oo ku noqnoqo. Ma dagteen jannada weli, ma durduuranteen malab. Dh: hirqo, rakaado.
dureemo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) geed cawseed meelaha dooxayada ah ku badan oo xooluhu gu' iyo jiilaal ba daaqaan oo ay ku cayilaan. Dameerihii waa kuwaa dureemada dooxa daaqaya. Dh: dareemo.
durfo: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) shey in badan jiray oo baali ah. Ilbaxnimada lagu diday, ma anigaa durfooboo, dawga toosan garab mara.
durfule: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) xayawaanka cayngalka ah ee baydada.
durguf: (falkaabe) marka noole si orod iyo booddo ku jirto meel uga soo baxo. Durguf buu doofaarkii igaga soo yihi ijaarka beerta.
durguf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) col jabay intii ka hadhay oo baydad ah ama firxad. Durgufkii ka hadhay gaaladaan doy ka ridayaaye.
duricaymeed: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) duray ku dhaca duurjoogta. Duricaymeed baan ka soo qaaday dalxiiskii shalay.
durid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax turqid ama mudid.
durki: (fal) meel durugsan wax gey. Dh: fogee. Li: dhawee.
durkid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel ama shey, ka fogaan oo u dhawaansho la'aan.
durkin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) fidinta bedka walaxi leedahay. Dh: ballaadhin. Li: koobid.
durmad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) birta xakamaha ku xidhan ee faraska afka laga geliyo marka la xakamaynayo. Doogna waa ka nijaasoo, durmaddaanu ku aasnay. Dh: birxakame.
durmi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) jaad haadda duusha ka mid ah oo Soomaalida badh aaminsan yahay, haddii uu ilmo yar dul maro inuu xanuun u horsaadayo.
durqamid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadal aan istaag lahayn. Dh: duryamid, dhawdhaw. Li: aamus.
durqan: (tilmaame) mid wax ku mudan yahay ama ku taagan yahay. Qodax baa ku durqan yarka ee ka goo. Dh: mudsan, turqan.
durqumo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hadhaaga mooyaha gunta kaga dhegta marka lagu budlinayo raashinka.
durqun: (fal) cid kale dhibaato dhaawac ku ah u geyso. Dadka ma durqumo mana daandaansado. Dh: durree.
Durqun: magac loo baxsho gabadh dhalatay reerka oo buuq iyo khilaaf jiro.
durraamad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) bahal lagu ciyaaro oo la isku maaweeliyo xilliyada firaaqad ah. Durraamad bay ciyaarayaan wiilashii.
durraansi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) hadal aan raalli laga ahayn oo la isku celceliyo.
durraaxad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) marada lagu dul goglo furaashka ama sariirta. Durraaxadda ka beddel sariirta oo mid nadiif ah saar.
durraaxadee: (fal) go' ku gogol sariir ama furaash.
durrayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) waxyeellada jinku u gaysto insiga.
durraysi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) marka ay cidi muujiso dareen ah inay wax dhibsanayso. Kuuma fiicna durraysigu ee bishaarayso.
durriimo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) mudniin ku samayn. Dh: turqin, mudniin, irbadayn.
durrin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) kayn weyn oo duur leh. Durrimaha agtoodaba ha marin yey ku daakhiline.
durriyad: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qofku dadka uu dhalo ee ifka kaga hadha. Nebi ismaaciil waa durriyaddii nebi ibraahin. Dh: waraso.
durro: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax dhib leh. Durro ayuu sigaarku u leeyahay caafimaadka guud iyo ka gaar ba. Dh: dhibaato.
durrujaa: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) wixii dhulka ka soo taagan ee lagu turunturrooda oo dhan. Durrujaa baan lugta la helay oo aan ku kufay.
durrujaa -ga: (magac, lab, keli) geed da' weyn oo aan koritaan fiican lahayn. Durrujaa gaboobiyo, xume laga diqoodiyo, ma wixii dorraataa?
durruq: durruq-a: (magac, lab, keli), neef, cudur iyo da la tabar darreeyey.
durruqaan: durruqaan -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadal edebdarro ku jirto oo qof aan xishoonayni ku hadlo.
durruqiso: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gabadha mudda dadka buka.
durub: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) jaad kalluunka badda laga soo saaro ka mid ah.
durug: (fal) meel dheer teg. Dhankaa iiga durug aan fadhiistee. Dh: siko, fogow
durugso: (fal) ka sii kordhiso intii hore, meeshi hore ka jiido ama ka qaado. Durugso haragga hadhka tag.
dururuqlee: (fal) si macnodarro ah iskaga hadal Dururuqlee sidii qof aan fayoobayn. Dh: tororoglee.
dururuqleyn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka qof hadal aan macno lahayn kala joojin waayo. Dh: tororoglayn
duruuf: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) waayaha nolosha ku xeeran.
duryan: (fal) hadal aan loo fiirsan ama aan macno lahayn oo fara badan ku hadal. Dh: yulqan.
duryan -ka: (magac, lab, keli) hadal badan oo aan micno lahayn.
dus: (fal) meel daloosha ka dhex bax; dhex mar meel dalool ku yaallo.
dusaa: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) meeraha koowaad ee cadceedda u xiga. Dusaaga iyo dayaxa, dusaagaa cadceedda uga dhow.
dusdus: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) socod qarsoodi ah oo kolba dhinac loogu kaco. Dh: muutamuutayn.
dusi: (fal) si qarsoodi ah, wax meel uga saar.
dusi: (fal) meel cidhiidhi ah, wax hoosta ka mari.
dusid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof meel ka gaaban hoos maraya ama u bixitaanka si qarsoodi ah.
dusin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) qarsoodi wax isugu dhiibid.
dusmayn: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) si aan la dareemi karin, wax u samayn.
dusmo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) si aan cidi arkin u marid meel ama u gelid. Dusmo ayuu ku soo galay gudaha.
duu: (ereydhawaaq) la adeegsado marka awrka la celinayo. Duu dheh awrka. Dh: dooh.
duub: (fal) wax fidsan isku laablaab. Aloolka duub oo meel ku tiiri. Dh: giringiri. Li: fidi.
duub -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cimaamad iyo wixii la mid ah oo raggu madaxa ku duubtaan. Culimadii hore waxa lagu yaqiin duub.
duub -ka: (magac, lab, keli) bir wareegsan oo gacanta dumarku gashado inta badanna ka samaysan naxaas. Inanta duub u geli oo da'deed raaci. Dh: jijin.
duub -ka: (magac; lab, keli) nin beeshiisu u soo dooratay inuu madax u noqdo oo uu u taliyo. Dh: bogor, hoggaandhaqameed, malaaq, wabar, ugaas, suldaan, islaam.
duubashi: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) rarada, kabadda iyo aloolka hablaha gashaantimuhu samaystaan ee u duuban ilaa ay ka guri gelayaan.
duubcas: -ta: (magacwadareed) waax ka mid ahayd ciidamada qalabka sida ee Soomaaliya.
duubi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) muruqa ku yaalla lafaha dhaadheer ee daboola.
duubis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) isku laablaabka walax fidsanayd. Li: fidin.
duubo: (fal) laablaabo wax aad leedahay oo fidsanaa. Duubo gogoshaada oo meel dhigo. Dh: fidso.
duud: (tilmaame) gar adag oo dixda loola dhaadhaco oo dhiig ama dhaqaaqil lagu furdaaminayo.
duud-da: (magac, dhedig, keli) meel geedo badan oo is wada haysta oo aan si fudud loo mari karin. Dh: kayn, juuq, xidh, hilo, ay.
duud-ka: (magac, lab, keli) lafta dheer ee dhabarka. Duudka ayaa Kayd xanuunaya oo ma foorarsan karo.
duudgale: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) noolaha ku nool meesha kaynta jiqda ah.
duudi: (fal) weel biyo yar oo salkiisa ku haray ka shubid.
duud'oogeed: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) oogo dhadhaab Ishiileed ah, inta badan ufuq ahaan, wuxuu samaysmaa marka magma soo herdiyo laba lakab oo dhadhaab lakabeed dhexdood oo halkaa ku qaboobo kuna adkaado; qaradiidu waxay gaadhi kartaa xoogaa sentimitirro ah ama dhowr boqol mitir, laakiin ufuqiisu inta badan wuu ka weynyahay marka la barbardhigo qaradiisa.
duudsi: (fal) xaq qof uu lahaa weysii ama muran ka geli. Dh: dulmi.
duudsi -ga: (magac, lab, keli) cid waxay leedahay loo diido hadal qof yidhi oo uu iska diido. Dh: dafiraadda.
duudsiyid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax qof xaq u leeyahay badheedhe ugu diidid.
duuduub: duuduub -ka: (magac, lab, keli) isku laallaabnida wax fidsanaa.
duuduubid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) wax fidsanaa, isku laallaabid. Dh: duubid.
duudyow: (fal) neef xoolo ah, xummad la jiifi waa.
duudyow -ga: (magac, lab, keli) xumad noolaha u diidda jiif iyo joog oo ay la harjadaan.
duuf: (fal) bakhti oo naftu ha kaa baxdo.
duuf: (fal) dhimashada horteed noqo qof aan macno lahayn. Naga tag duuf ku baxe.
duuf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) neef isaga oo aan la xalaalayn dhintay.
duuf -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dareere ka yimaadda sanka. Nin duray hayo duuf lagama waayo. Dh: siin.
duufaan: -ka: (magac, lab, kali) roob iyo dabayl xoog leh oo is wata. Duufaan baa dumiyey daarihii magaalada.
duufaanonkodle: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) duufaan maayado hawo sare oo xooggan leh, oo sameeya daruuro kumuloonimbas ah oo aad u kobocsan, oo leh dhibco aad u waaweyn, oo yeelan kara baraf dhagax ah, kolkaa danab qulqulka sameysmaa bhaliyo hillaacyo, iyo onkod ka dhashay fididda hawada kulka badan e hilaaca darteed.
duufi: (fal) qof kale sankiisa ka bi'i dareeraha ku jira oo ka nadiifi. Dh: siimi.
duuflaal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) nin doqon ah oo aan talo rag la weydiin. Dh: nacas, caran coon, doqon, dabbaal. Li: fariid, geesi.
duufle: -ha: (tilmaame) nin doqon ah oo had iyo jeer sankiisu qoyanyahay. Dh: siinle.
duufsasho: duufsasho -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale, wax ku qancin oo madaxa ka qabsasho.
duufsi: -ga: (magac, lab, keli) si aan daacad ahayn, dad kale wax ugu sheegid oo ku qancin.
duufsi-ga: (magac, lab, keli) siinsiga geelu siinsado isaga oo naqas weyn sanka si xoog ah uga soo tuuraya.
duufso: (fal) cid kale, si qalad ah ugu qanci in ra'yigaaga ay raacdo.
duufso: (fal) siin iska bi'i oo sanka nadiifso.
duug: (fal) meel jidhka ka mid ah gacanta ku jijibi.
duug: (fal) neef xoolo ah oo caano badan ku leh ka lis.
duug: (fal) wax, yaanuu muuqane qari oo intaad god u qoddo ciidda ku rog.
duug: (fal) qof geeriyooday xabaal oo meel qodan ku aas. Dh: aas, xabaal.
duug-ga: (magac, lab, keli) wax in badan jirey oo gaboobay. Dh: hun, gabow. Li: cusub, da'yar.
duug -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) kharashka ku baxa aaska meydka.
duugan: (tilmaame) wax la duugay oo jidhkiisa gacanta la mariyay. Lugtu way i duugan tahaye ha i taaban.
duugan: (tilmaame) wax aasan oo dhulka ku hoos jira. Qabrigaa awawgay baa ku duugan. Dh: aasan, xabaalan.
duugato: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xiddigta Gogolduub oo ah mid la baasaysto.
duugduug: (fal) duug oo gacanta kolba dul marmari.
duugduugid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) hab tuutuujin iyo salaaxid iskugu jira oo jidhka daalka lagaga saaro.
duugduugis: -ta: (magac, dhedig,keli) jidhka, meel xidid hayo, kolba gacanta marin oo kala bixin.
duugid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) faraha si farsamo iyo khibradi ku jirto jidhka ugu jijibin oo xididdada iyo muruqyada ku furfurid.
duugid -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qof dhintay, qabri ku aasid. Duugidda maydka laguma raago.
duugmid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) baabi'id oo wax dabargo'ay noqosho. Dh: dabargu'id.
duugmo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) jidhka oo dufan la mariyo oo gacanta lagu duugo.
duugmo -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qalab badanaa caw ka samaysan oo dhulka lagu haro, qashinkana lagu xaadho. Dh: dhulfiiq, minfiiq.
duugnaansho: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qof la duugay ahaan.
duugoobid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) gaboobid darteed wax burburaya noqosho. Dh: baaliyoobid.
duugow: duugow -ga: (magac, lab, keli) mar walaxi baali noqoto oo uu muddo badan jiro. Dh: baaliyoow.
duul: (fal) weerar dagaal qaad. Labadii beelood beel baa lagu duulay.
duul: (fal) samada mar oo sare u haad.
duul -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dir ama dad isku asal ah. Dh: dir.
duul-sha: (magac, dhedig, keli) xawayaan weyn oo agdaaga biyaha webiyada iyo haraha laga helo. Dh: jeer.
duulaan: wiil dhashay xilli uu aabihii duullaan tegayay ama ku maqnaa. Waxa kale oo loo baxshaa wiil la rajaynayo in uu noqdo mid cadawga ku duula.
duulduul: duulduul-ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax dheeftiisu aanay ku soo wada gaarin laakiin wax yari kaa soo gaaro.
duulduulid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) shinbir iyo wixii la mid ah, kolba dhan u lalid. Ayax duulduulid ma daayo. Dh: lallid.
Duule: ama Duulaan, wiil dhashay xilli uu aabihii duullaan tegayay ama ku maqnaa. Waxa kale oo loo baxshaa wiil la rajaynayo in uu noqdo mid duula oo cadawga weerara.
duuli: (fal) diyaarad ama wax kale oo duula oo degsanaa kici oo samada u dir. Duuli diyaaradda oo dubay gee. Li: deji.
duulid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) marka noole taagnida ka kaco ama uu duulo. Aboodigu waa shinbir duulid badan.
duulin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) shinbir, diyaarad iyo wax la mid ah, hawada u dirid. Dh: haadin. Li: dejin, fadhiisin.
duulista: (magac, dhedig, keli) hawada lalid; cirka u kicid. Dh: duulid.
duulis: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) cid kale oo colaadi idinka dhaxayso, weerar ku qaadid.
duulitaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dhulka ka kicid oo hawada dhex jibaaxid.
duulitaan-ka: (magac, lab, keli) cid kale oo colaadi idinka dhaxayso, weerar ku qaadid.
duuliye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) qofka duuliya ee kexeeya diyaaradaha.
duullaan: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) cid kale, col ku bixin oo weerar qaadid.
Duullane: magac loo baxsho wiil dhiirran oo duullimaadka iyo hawsha u heellan oo aan loo dirin.
duullimaad: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) socdaalka uu ku jiro wax samada maraya. Duulimaad bay diyaaraddii weli ku jirtaa.
duumaale: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) milay ama meel ay duumo dad badan ku laysay.
duumadhawr: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) daawada lagaga hortago duumada. Dh: kahortag.
duumo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xanuunka laga qaado qaniiyada kaneecada.
duun: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) dunida iyo waxa kor saaran. Dh: adduun.
duun -ka: (magac, lab, keli) naf ama ruux iyo nolol. Ninkan fulaha ah, duun kuma jiro naxdin baa naftii ka saartay.
duunkiye: -ha: (magac, lab, keli) mid muraad leh ama ujeeddo leh. Dh: danle.
duunkiyeel: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wuxuu doonaba yeele. Dh: danayste.
duunyo: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) xoolaha ama hantida uu qof leeyahay. Dh: hanti.
duunyodhaqato: -da: (magacwadareed) dadka ku nool miyiga ee xoolaha nool xanaanaysta.
duunyodhaqid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) qaabka xoolaha loo xannaaneeyo ee daranyada looga ilaaliyo.
duur: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) meel aan la degganayn oo ay ah.

duur-ka: (magac, lab, keli) caws dhuudhuuban oo adayg badan leh iyo xubno oo dhaadheer oo burbur u baxa lagana sameeyo aloolka iyo wixii la mid ah. Dad iyo duur ba waxaanad filayn baa kaagaga soo baxa.
duurduur: (fal) macno la'aan iska socsoco oo meelahaa kolba dhan u wareeg. Dh: warwareeg, meermeer.
duurgal: -ka: (magac, lab, keli) wax kaynta iska xula oo dibadgal noqda. Dh: dibadgale.
duurgelid: -da: (magac, dhedig, keli) kaynta xulid oo wax dibad meer ah noqosho. Odayga cadho ayaa duurgelidda ugu wacan. Dh: duurxulid.
duurin: -ta: (magac, dhedig, keli) astaan ama summad dhegta hasha lagu dhigo oo in yar caarada laga saro.
duurjoog: -ta: (magacwaareed) xayawaanka aan la rabbayn ee ku nool ayda. Dh: ugaad. Li: docjoog, dabjoog.
duurxul: (fal) hadal ujeeddo qarsoon leh qof si sarbeeb ah ugu sheeg. Dh: cayngal.

aafo: n6-f, n8-f • disaster, severe damage (period of natural disaster: hurricane, flood, plague, etc.) Aafaadka soconaaya Eebbow naga duw! God, save us from the present disasters!
aaga: -aaga Variant: -kaaga pro-det-2sg • your shaahaaga your tea.

aalad: n1-f • weapon; instrument; machine; equipment; mechanism; technology; apparatus

aallee: v4c-1sg-pot • I may be (in a place)
aallo: v4c-1sg-opt • let me be (in a place)
aalo: n6-f-col • heifer, young female cattle; heifers
aammiin: n2-f • amen; [intj] so be it, may it be so!
aammin: aammin1 v1= • have faith, trust, confide in, believe
aammin2 n2-m • honest person; [atr.] trustworthy, reliable, sincere
aammin3 n2-m • peaceful place without danger
aamminsan: adj-der • trusting, having faith in, believing
aamminsanow: v3a= • trust, have faith in, believe in
aammus: aammus1 v1= • be silent, keep quiet, shut up
aammus2 Compare: hus, shib, us vn2-m, vn7-m • silence.
aammusnaan: n0-f-abs • silence, state of being silent
aan: aan1 neg-rel • not Alt of ma in relative clauses shaqada aan la qabaneynin the work which wont be done
-aan1 v3a-inch-inf • become, get [INCHOATIVE] Waa markii iigu horreysey halka. This is my first time here.
-aan2 n8-pl-suf • [IRREGULAR PLURAL] tagayaa I am going qorayaa he is writing
-aan3 n-f-abs-suf • -ness, -ment Derives an abstract noun from an adjective caadahaan traditional Caadadeeda ma jecli. I don't like her way of doing things.
-aan4 v1-3pl-neg-prhb • they do not (X) Basal mey cunaan. They don't eat onions.
-aan5 v1-3pl-prhb • they do (X) cunaan they eat
-aan6 v5a-neg-opt • may [someone] not be ... Yaaney foolxumaan! May she not be ugly!
aanad: aanad2 neg + vpro • you ... not = aan + aad Shaqada aanad qabanin wey adagtahay. The work you didnt do is difficult.
aanan: vpro + neg • I ... not = aan + aan
aanay: neg + vpro • she / it [fem] ... not; they ... not = aan + ay
aanaysi: Compare: waaceensi vn7-m • blame, act of blaming, holding someone responsible
aanee: v2b= • blame, accuse, resent, hold responsible for; charge with; seek revenge
aannan: vpro + neg • we [excl] ... not = aannu + aan Saacad aannan shaqeynin lacag nala ma siiyo. We are not paid for an hour that we have not worked.
aannee: -aannee v5a-1pl-pot • suppose we may be ..., what if we are ...? Sow jeclaannee? Suppose we like it?
aanneen: -aanneen v5a-1pl-neg-cond • we would not have been. Maannu ogaanneen We would not have known.
aannin: -aannin v5a-neg-opt • may [someone] not be ... Yaanu ogaannin! Dont let him be aware of it!
aanno: -aanno v5a-1pl-opt • may we be, let us be ... Haddii uun aynu ladnaanno! If only we would be healthy!
aansho: -aansho vn6-m-st-suf • state of being (X); -ation [GERUND] Makes a masculine stative verbal noun toddobaadkii dambe last week sannadkii dambe last year; Contrast: -ka.
aanu: 1 neg + vpro • he ... not = aan + uu.
aar: aar1 n4-m • adult male lion; [fig.] brave man
aar2 Compare: saajac vn0-m-col • revenge, vengeance.
aaraa': n8-f-pl • ideas, opinions; [ext.] preface, introduction (of a book)
aarad: n1-f • edge ~ border of an Arab robe
aaradee: v2b=tr • make the border for something (e.g., clothes)
aaran: aaran1 n0-m-abs • abundance of water and green grass; prosperity, flourishing natural environment
aaran2 n2a-m-col • young camels who are no longer sucklings, camel youth
aargalaan: n2-m • large cup ~ glass; metal cup with a handle
aarsasho: vn6-f • vengeance, act of taking revenge
aas: -aas deic-m-suf • that, those On masculine nouns
aas1 n4-m • colorful light of sunset.
aasan: aasan1 v1=inch • be buried, get buried
aashaa: np / adv • you ... slowly, gently, carefully
aashay: np / adv • I ... slowly, gently, carefully Aashay baan u akhriyey. I read it carefully.
aasheed: np / adv • she ... slowly, gently, carefully Aasheed bay hilibkii u karisay. She cooked the meat slowly.
aashuun: n2-m • water-jar made of clay; jug
aatee: -aatee v5a-2sg/3f-pot • suppose you are / so she may be ...
aateen: -aateen1 v5a-2pl-opt • may you all be! Waan filayaa in aydin jeclaateen! I hope that you like it!
-aateen2 v5a-2pl-pot • suppose you all are / so you may be ...
-aateen3 v5a-neg-cond • you / she would not have been.
aato: -aato v5a-2sg/3f-opt • may you / she be Maxaad ku tashateen? What did you decide on? Ku tasho inaad ila joogto. Count on staying at my place.
aawadeed: np / conj • because of, for its sake After a feminine noun Tigidh la'aan awadeed ayaan u tegi waayey. I failed to go because I didn't have a ticket.'
aawadiis: Compare: aw np / conj • because of, for its sake After a masculine noun Roob badan awadiis wadooyiinkii oo dhan daad baa xidhay. Because of heavy rain, a flood closed all the streets.
aaway: aaway1 qw-loc-m • where is he / it [masc]?
aawo: n0-f • sake, reason Used with possessive pronouns
aay: -aay1 name-f-voc-suf • hey you! [FEMININE VOCATIVE] Used to call or address a female barad trainee dhunkad act of kissing haysad possessing.
aayad: aayad2 Compare: mucjiso n1-f • miracle, wonder
aayar: Compare: aad yar Adverb • slowly, gently, lightly, slightly
aaye: aaye1 n6-f • aunt, uncle's wife; stepmother
aayeen: -aayeen v5a-3pl-past • they were Wey fiicnaayeen. They were fine.
aayo: aayo4 n6-f • aunt, uncle's wife; stepmother
ab: ab1 n4-m, n7-m • ancestor; [pl] forefathers, ancestry.
ab2 n2-m-cmp, n7-m • native (of a place); locals; tradition, heritage.
abaab: v1= • scatter on; crawl, creep, move along by creeping; walk (as reptile ~ insect).

a: df.art., the, (af) used with its support.
á, ad., this, that, (af) used with its support.
aal: or ahal, f.n., slime or viscous matter mixed with blood (in dysentery).—shi.
‘ab: v.tr., drink (this verb is used for any liquid except milk, coffee, and broth); biyaha “ab, drink water; dawada ‘ab, drink the medicine; biyo ‘ab o hamri iss ka da, drink water and not wine; biyaha la 'ab, the water is drunk.
‘absi: v.c., cause or give to drink ; i ‘absi, make me or give me to drink.
'abād: m.n., camels grunting (while its burden is fastened on). —ki; aur ‘abādked ma je‘li, I do not like the camel’s grunting.
abah: m.n., time of birth.—hi: hashi nerig bai abahha ku dashai or dalatai, the she-camel brought forth her young one.
abaḥ: m.n., lean animal. —hi; aurkasi wa geli abaḥah, that camel is lean.
abaḥ, v.i., be lean ;wu abiḥi, he will be lean.
‘abai: v.tr., load a gun; bunduha ‘abai, load the gun.
abāl: m.n., gratitude, acknowledgment, remuneration, requital. —ki; abālka ān ku (pi. idin) habo or haiyo weligi wu jiri, my gratitude for you will last forever; hadiyadda an ku so diro wa abālkan ku haba or haiya, the gift I send you is an acknowledgment; wa abalké, it is your requital; abal u hab, be grateful; abal ban ad ugu habai or abal ada yan u habai, I was very grateful to him; wahhasi wa abalkai, it is for my gratitude.
abālgud: u abālgud, v.tr., reward; i abālgud, reward me; wan ku abālgudai, I rewarded you.
abālgudi: v.tr., reward (only used by some, especially by people from the west)
abālmari: v.tr., be grateful, thank, reward. —ya or abālmarsha, —wan n; aniga abbaha abālmariyai, I was grateful to the father.
abar: f.n., drought, sterility, famine. —ti ; bilad somalied abar ba ka da'dai or bilad somalied o dami abar wa lehyahai, there is everywhere drought in the Somali country; wa abar, there is famine; abarta meshas ka da'dai ad ba lo ogyahai, the sterility of that place is well known.
abba: m.n., father. —hi ; aiya abba, or abbai, or abbo! my father.
abban: m.n.f friend, protector, guide, conductor. —ki; (guest and host are abban;) abban dulai, m.n., chief, leader.
abbanso: v.r., become friends with ; ninkas abbanso, put yourself under the protection of that man, or become friends with that man.
'abbar: m.n., moment, short time, a while. —ki; 'abbar jog, wait a moment ; 'abbar la hadso, sit a moment with him.
abhad: f.n., small box made with the bark of trees tacked together. —di.
abho: f.n., fruit of a thorny tree called huda', of which sheep and goats are very fond.
abid: and abki, ad., never (these words are never employed alone as given, but inflected according to the person speaking or spoken of (s. gram.).
abodi: m.n., large bird of prey, having a red beak and red legs. —gi
abor: m.n., Bpeoies of white ants making their hills or houses in the desert. —ki.
'abso: v.i., be afraid or frightened. —da, wan —n.
'absileh: a., dangerous, perilous; war! mel 'absileh ina gei, take us to a dangerous place.
abti: m.n., maternal uncle. —gi; or hoyada walalked, the mother's brother.
abtirsinyo: m.n., genealogy. -hi; 'Issa abtirsinyihisi, the genealogy of Jesus.
‘abud: v.tr., adore ; ha lagu 'abudo, be thou adored.
abud: v.tr., shut, close (employed lor small boxes), cork a bottle abhadda abud, shut or close the box ; haruradda abud.
'abud: v.tr., suffocate ('abudi is also used by some).
abur: m. or f.n., behaviour, conduct, temper. —ki or —ti; aburkisu wa side? how does he behave? aburkisu wa sida, he behaves so; abur fi'an, good temper; abur hun, bad temper.
aburan: v.p., be produced, created; aburma, wan abtirmi, wan aburmai, I was created.
aburan, m.n., creation. —ki; aburnin. —ti, f.n., is also used.
aburan, a.v., created; wah aburan, a created thing.
ad: a. and ad., well, nice, good, loud, strong (this word is an adverb when u is added to it. Ex. kitabkas wa ad, that book is nice; ad u tol, sew well; ad u hadal, speak well or loudly; ad u adkai, make it strongly; ad u dis, build well.
'ad: m.n., piece of meat, flesh. —ki (the plural 'adad is not used by all) ; 'adki i dib, give me the piece of meat ; 'adki i wada ken or 'adadki i ken, bring me the pieces of meat.
'adaw: v.att., be, become white (no imperative) ; wan 'adan. (When this verb is used in the imperative, it is a kind of curse.)
'adaisnaw: v.att., remain or be white, clean; distigu wa 'adaisanyahai, the kettle is made white or cleansed.
'adaisan: a.v.,made white, cleansed; maro 'adaisan, clean linen.
'adab: f.n., hell. —ti. ; 'adab yar, purgatory. dab 'adabed, m.n., hell fire. —ki.
'adab or 'adib, v.tr., torment, torture; 'adab means also condemn to hell.
'adad: fn., kind of acacia tree with stiff and bent thorns, gum-tree. —di.
adad: m.n., excrescence of flesh in a sore. —ki.
'adadi: 'adadi, v.tr., press. (In the jungle Somals, when making their enclosure or fence round their huts, press together the trees cut for that purpose, in order that the branches may be straight, so as to form a close and tough hedge.)
adag: a., dear (price), fast firm, hard, strong, light, tough, permanent. (This word is used for things only.)
adkai: v.tr., fasten, strengthen, tighten, make strong. ha lagu adka, v.p., be fastened.
adkaw: v.att., be firm, strong, fastened. ka adkaw, v.a., overcome him, her; ka adka, he overcomes, overcame him ; ka adkatai, she overcomes, overcame ; wa laga adka, adkadai, he, she is overcome.
adai: m.n., arak tree (Capparis sodata), small stick used by Somals for cleaning their teeth. -gi.
'adanyo: 'adanyo or 'adanyod, v.i., have an itching. —da, wan —n.
'adar: 'adar, m.m., haziness, hazy weather, drizzling rain. —ki (no plur.) 'adar da, it drizzles or drizzling rain is falling.
adar: m.n., earthen pot with two handles in which food is cooked. —ki.
'ad'ed: f.n, rays of the sun, sun. —di; eg! 'ad'eddi da'dai, look! the sun is setting; war! 'ad'eddi so bahdai, ina kena, mesha ka so'onai, the rays of the sun appear, let us go away from the place. —di.
aderyo 'ari: lesser koodoo antelope (used for both genders). N.B. Somals generally make no difference between aderyo and aderyo 'ari. They call the males godir, and the females aderyo.
adin: adin, v.tr., call to prayer ; adima, wan adimi.
'aḋo: f.n., anger, indignation, rage, wrath (no plur.).
'ado, v.i., rage. —da, wan —n. u 'ado, v.tr., rage against.
'aḋaisi: with ka, v.c, provoke, make him angry, enrage.
af badan: a., sharp ; mindi af badan, a sharp knife.
af daran: a., blunt; mindidi afka daraid i ken, bring me the blunt knife.
afdub: afdub, m.n., closing of the mouth to prevent a man from crying out when they rob his cattle and sheep. —ki ; ninkas afdubkisi mid ad u aha, the gagging of that man was good.
af'eli: v.tr., interpret (this verb is used with uga, ka, or u ka la); wan u ka la af'elin, I interpret or I will interpret.
aftiro: v.tr., wipe your lips ; aftirta, wan aftiran. Somals also use aftiro for 'take some food.'
afyahan: m.n. and a., eloquent, eloquent man, tame. —ki; aniga afyahan miihi, I am not eloquent, or not an eloquent man; faras afyahan, a tame horse dinnad aftahan, a tame cat dinnaddi afkatihin, the tame cat.
afarr: n.c, four.—ti; afarr nagod, four women.
afrad: n.c.o., fourth; ki afrad (m.), the fourth.
afarr iyo tobnad: n.c.o., fourteenth, a fortnight ; afarr iyo tobnadki, the fortnight.
'affi: 'affi, m.n., forgiveness, pardon. —gi. war! iss 'affiya, v.r., pardon each other (plur.)
afimad: m.n., health. —ki; ma afimad habta? are you in good health? ha wa ladnahai, yes I am.
afo: f.n., woman, lady; afada serkalka, the wife of the governor.
afur: m.n., a small meal taken at about six o'clock in the evening during the time of fasting, while the muezzin is calling Mussulmans to prayer. The other meal, taken from 12 p.m. to 4 a.m. is called suhur.
'agta'ad: f.n., foot-sole; agti 'adaid, the sole of the foot.
ag: ad., near (this word is never used alone) ; agta, agtaida kalai, come near (me) ; agtisi tag, go near (to him).
agan: f.n., bark vessel (shaped like a double cone, and protected by a light framework of wood called sab). —ti.
agon: m.n., orphan boy. -ki (the plural for both sexes is agonadi).

agon, /.«., orphan girl. ti (this word is also used for both sexes) Berberah agonadu wa ku badanyihin, or Berberah agontu wa ku badantahai, or war Berberi wa agon badan tahai, there are many orphans in Berberah.
ah: (root) v., he (often used as an affix; scarcely ever alone).
ahaw: ha ahato, or ha ahatai e, loc. meaning nevertheless, never mind, be it so.
ahdi: m.n., oath, swearing, alliance, treaty made by an oath. -gi. ahdi Ebbahai inan ka kausin, I swear by God that I will kill you.

ahdi, v.tr., swear, make a treaty, an alliance grounded upon an oath; wa la iss ahdiyai o dagal ma jiro, I made a treaty that we may not fight; kal hore yainu iss ahdinai lakin ahdigi wa adigi beinaiyai, last year we made a treaty, but you perjured yourself, or you did not remain faithful to it.
ahal horti: m.n. fa9ade, house-front. -ki. ahalka hortisi bai jogan, or wa ku joga, they are before, or in front of, the house.
ahbal: or ka ahbal, v.tr., accept, listen to, receive (in addressing ourselves to God); Ilahow naga ahbal, O God, hear us Ilahhai dua'daida ha iga ahbalo, or dua'daida Ilah ha iga ahbalo, may God hear our prayers.
ahbal, with kaga, v.tr., kill ninki kaga ahbal, kill the man (used especially in quarrelling and fighting).
ahil: m.n., Somali chief, sage, respectable man. —ki; aḥilki Karin yan arkai shalai, yesterday I saw the chief of Karan; ahilo, or uḥul, or uḥal are also used. -ki; —shi; —shi.
'aïah: a..., cursed; eraigi ‘aïda aha, the cursed word.
'aï: v.tr., curse, abuse. —a, wan ‘aï, wan 'aïtamaya or wan ‘aïaya, I am cursing, abusing him.
'aïd: f.n., poor man (having nothing at all). —di.
a'imad: m.n., tame beast flying, running away. -ki. (They call so a camel which is not yet accustomed to carry loads, and is afraid.)
aiya!: int., used in the place of warya in speaking to the parents or other respectable persons aiya abba, abbe, or abbo! O father! aiya hoyo! or ai hoyo! O mother!
‘ajibi: v.tr., please, make glad somebody, consent to.
ajis: (m.) ‘ajisad (f.), n. and a, indolent, lazy. -ki; ajisin (plur.), ‘ajis, or 'ajisad ban ahai, I am lazy.
‘al: or ma'al, f.n., dew-lap (also used for Somali sheep).
‘ala'al: or ‘alaan'al, m.n., regret. sorrow (also the expression of regret you feel at being unable to help someone). 'ala’alkisi bu i siyai, he expressed to me his regret; inanka 'alaan’alkisi ba ku fogadai o la talin kari wainai, the sorrow of that child was so deep that we could not console him.
‘ala’al: with u, .., regret, repent; dembigaigi yan ad iyo ad ugu ‘ala'alsanahai, Lrepent heartily of my sins.
‘alaa’al: or 'alaan'al, f.n., palm of the hand, -shi.
‘ala‘al: m.n., a person deprived of all his goods and fortune.
'ala’al: v., be deprived of, lose; bai! bai! 'ala'alaieh ho gai o ho gail exclamation of sorrow, the crying of women when beaten, I lost all!
‘alan: m.n., flag, ensign.—ki; hori alan, flagstaff
‘alen: f.n., leaf, leaves (also used for tea). -ti.
‘alid: v.i., fester, grow virulent; hontisu malin walba wa si ‘alidaisa, his sore is growing more virulent every day. (For a sore becoming worse, see Aid. When there is an excresence of flesh they say adad.)

abwaanno.name: Abwaan Urursan (Qaamuus Af-Soomaali - Af-Ruush) - D. I. Estebanyenko, Maxamed Xaaji Cismaan [1969]

aad: очень, весьма; вполне; ~ iyo ~ очень, сильно; понастоящему.

aa': v. tr. 1 (ay, day) 1. Minacciare qn.; colpire qn. o qs.; aggredire qn. 2. Is a.: combattere; scontrarsi; azzuffarsi.
aa: aa2 pr. cl. so. 1. vr. di aad'. 2. vr. di aydin.
aa³ es. - Ahi!; ah! (per esprimere dolore).
aabayeel: aabayeel v. it. 1 (-eelay, -eeshay) - U a.: dare importanza a qs., avere interesse per qs.
aabayeelid: nv. f. di aabayeel?. vr. aabayeel'.
aabbe: n. m. (-bayaal, m. of.)- 1. Padre. 2. Il pl. anche: antenati.
aabbur: n. m. (-rro, f) - Coperchio concavo che viene inserito nell'apertura del recipiente e non appoggiato.
aabbur2 v. tr. I (-ray, -rtay) Tappare qs.; chiudere o coprire con un coperchio qs.
aabburan: v. it. 1 (-rmay, -rantay; -rmi) - Venire tappato; venire chiuso o coperto con un coperchio.
aabburan2 v. it. 4 (-rnaa, -rnayd) - Essere tappato; essere chiuso o coperto con un coperchio.
aabburnaan: nv. f. di aabburan?, vr. aabburnaansho.
aabburnaansho: n. m. of. vr. di aabburnaan.

aabiweyrax: n. m. (-xyo, f.)- Reazione violenta, aggressione ingiustificata.
aabyoo: v. it. 3 (-ooday, -ootay) - Ku a.: offendere qn., fare una prepotenza a qn., essere arrogante con qn.
